02:08:52,906 --> 02:08:55,898
<i>You were walking home from school,</i>

2009
02:08:55,976 --> 02:08:58,171
<i>and they told you
they needed help finding a dog.</i>

2010
02:08:58,245 --> 02:08:59,507
<i>Yeah.</i>

2011
02:08:59,579 --> 02:09:02,639
<i>So, after you got in the truck,
what happened next?</i>

2012
02:09:02,716 --> 02:09:05,014
<i>They drove me around for a long time,</i>

2013
02:09:05,085 --> 02:09:06,643
then we ended up at this ranch.

2014
02:09:06,786 --> 02:09:10,187
Come on. Come on, Davy.

2015
02:09:10,257 --> 02:09:11,622
- Davy! Come on.
- Get off me.

2016
02:09:11,691 --> 02:09:12,885
Don't fight this much. Hey!

2017
02:09:12,959 --> 02:09:15,052
Were there other boys there?

2018
02:09:15,762 --> 02:09:18,230
<i>Yeah. Five, I think.</i>

2019
02:09:19,799 --> 02:09:21,733
It was a long time ago, though.

2020
02:09:21,801 --> 02:09:24,099
Hello, boys.
This is Davy.

2021
02:09:24,170 --> 02:09:25,535
I know you'll make him feel...
Hey!

2022
02:09:26,706 --> 02:09:30,039
No. No! Hey! Shut up!

2023
02:09:30,110 --> 02:09:32,010
Did you speak to them?

2024
02:09:32,779 --> 02:09:35,373
Yeah? You remember any of their names?

2025
02:09:36,249 --> 02:09:38,217
Yeah.

2026
02:09:38,285 --> 02:09:39,718
Two of them were brothers.

2027
02:09:39,786 --> 02:09:42,619
I think their last name was Winslow.

2028
02:09:43,924 --> 02:09:46,017
<i>The oldest one was Jeffrey.</i>

2029
02:09:49,996 --> 02:09:51,486
And Walter.

2030
02:09:53,900 --> 02:09:55,424
<i>Walter?</i>

2031
02:09:56,202 --> 02:09:59,103
- Yeah.
- Do you remember Walter's last name?

2032
02:10:04,544 --> 02:10:05,806
Collins.

2033
02:10:07,480 --> 02:10:09,038
<i>Walter Collins.</i>

2034
02:10:10,083 --> 02:10:13,314
Tell me something if you only remember
some of the boys' names,

2035
02:10:13,386 --> 02:10:16,048
how come you remember his full name?

2036
02:10:16,790 --> 02:10:18,917
Because of what happened.

2037
02:10:18,992 --> 02:10:21,017
<i>Walter and Jeffrey were talking.</i>

2038
02:10:21,094 --> 02:10:23,028
<i>- Pull it.
- They kept checking around</i>

2039
02:10:23,096 --> 02:10:25,690
and they found a part of the coop
where the wire was all messed up.

2040
02:10:25,765 --> 02:10:27,357
Be careful!

2041
02:10:27,434 --> 02:10:29,129
Hurry!

2042
02:10:29,202 --> 02:10:31,568
Maybe make enough room
to get out of there and run.

2043
02:10:31,638 --> 02:10:33,333
When we get out, we split up,

2044
02:10:33,406 --> 02:10:35,169
go in different directions. Okay?

2045
02:10:35,241 --> 02:10:37,334
They can't catch all of us.

2046
02:10:37,410 --> 02:10:39,378
It'd make an awful lot of noise.

2047
02:10:39,446 --> 02:10:42,176
Be quiet. You got it?

2048
02:10:42,248 --> 02:10:45,149
And if it wasn't wide enough,
then we'd be stuck.

2049
02:10:48,521 --> 02:10:51,718
Wait.
Help! Help! Come on, hurry!

2050
02:10:52,626 --> 02:10:55,925
My foot's stuck!
Hurry, help! Help me, please!

2051
02:10:58,498 --> 02:11:01,365
He's coming!
He's...

2052
02:11:01,434 --> 02:11:03,095
My foot!

2053
02:11:04,037 --> 02:11:05,561
He's coming.

2054
02:11:05,639 --> 02:11:07,402
Hurry, run, run, run!

2055
02:11:12,512 --> 02:11:15,003
Hey! What the hell are you boys...

2056
02:11:16,883 --> 02:11:21,513
Oh! Mary, Mother of God!
Hey! Hey! Hey!

2057
02:11:22,255 --> 02:11:25,315
You get back here!
Hey! Hold it! Hey!

2058
02:11:27,794 --> 02:11:28,886
Hey!

2059
02:11:30,063 --> 02:11:31,121
Hey!

2060
02:11:32,332 --> 02:11:33,959
Stop!

2061
02:11:36,302 --> 02:11:37,667
Check on the others!

2062
02:11:37,737 --> 02:11:39,136
Stop! Damn it!

2063
02:11:39,205 --> 02:11:41,469
Boys, I'm coming after you!

2064
02:11:41,541 --> 02:11:44,635
Damn it! Damn it!

2065
02:11:44,944 --> 02:11:47,879
Boys, I'll find you no matter where you are!

2066
02:11:47,947 --> 02:11:50,313
- They're not in there!
- Come on! Get in the car!

2067
02:11:50,383 --> 02:11:54,513
I'm gonna find you!
Damn it! Damn it! Come on.

2068
02:11:54,587 --> 02:11:56,987
Shit! Get in the car, Sanford!

2069
02:12:04,464 --> 02:12:07,092
That was the last I saw of any of them.

2070
02:12:07,667 --> 02:12:10,693
So, you don't know
if either of the other two were captured?

2071
02:12:10,770 --> 02:12:11,862
No.

2072
02:12:13,139 --> 02:12:15,039
All I know is,

2073
02:12:15,108 --> 02:12:17,975
if Walter hadn't come back for me

2074
02:12:18,845 --> 02:12:21,575
<i>I don't think I ever
would've gotten out of there.</i>

2075
02:12:22,482 --> 02:12:23,847
Okay.

2076
02:12:25,118 --> 02:12:27,279
So, what happened after that?

2077
02:12:27,353 --> 02:12:29,048
I kept off the main roads,

2078
02:12:29,122 --> 02:12:34,082
until I saw a train stopped at a crossing
and I jumped in.

2079
02:12:34,494 --> 02:12:37,554
Why didn't you tell anyone what had happened?

2080
02:12:37,630 --> 02:12:39,097
I was afraid.

2081
02:12:39,599 --> 02:12:42,568
I thought they'd come after me, or my folks.

2082
02:12:44,370 --> 02:12:46,804
<i>So, I just didn't tell anybody.</i>

2083
02:12:48,675 --> 02:12:52,873
I was on my own until I got a free meal
from this lady, Miss Lansing.

2084
02:12:52,946 --> 02:12:55,437
Told her I was an orphan, on my own.

2085
02:12:57,417 --> 02:12:59,408
She said I could stay on.

2086
02:13:00,854 --> 02:13:02,185
And I did.

2087
02:13:03,423 --> 02:13:04,788
<i>Every night,</i>

2088
02:13:04,858 --> 02:13:08,294
I'd wake up thinking
they were right outside my window.

2089
02:13:08,828 --> 02:13:11,296
And then I heard the police
talking on the radio

2090
02:13:11,364 --> 02:13:14,128
about what happened at the ranch.

2091
02:13:14,234 --> 02:13:16,600
And I thought,
"For sure I can't go back now."

2092
02:13:16,669 --> 02:13:18,136
Why?

2093
02:13:18,671 --> 02:13:19,729
Why not?

2094
02:13:19,806 --> 02:13:22,604
Since I didn't tell anybody what happened.

2095
02:13:23,977 --> 02:13:26,741
I was afraid they'd blame me
for those kids being dead.

2096
02:13:28,648 --> 02:13:30,513
So I just stayed away.

2097
02:13:32,252 --> 02:13:35,244
What made you come forward now,
after all this time?

2098
02:13:35,321 --> 02:13:37,881
Hmm? Why come forward now?

2099
02:13:41,461 --> 02:13:43,224
I really miss my mom.

2100
02:13:45,632 --> 02:13:47,532
I really miss my dad.

2101
02:13:50,570 --> 02:13:52,538
I just wanna go home.

2102
02:13:55,942 --> 02:13:57,739
<i>I just wanna go home.</i>

2103
02:14:03,750 --> 02:14:05,513
Are you all right?

2104
02:14:06,186 --> 02:14:08,381
I love you.

2105
02:14:40,887 --> 02:14:42,650
I still can't believe it.

2106
02:14:42,722 --> 02:14:46,624
Five years, case closed,
everyone thinks he's dead, and there he is.

2107
02:14:48,127 --> 02:14:50,891
Wouldn't be, if it wasn't for Walter.

2108
02:14:52,565 --> 02:14:55,125
Your son did a brave thing, Mrs. Collins.

2109
02:14:55,201 --> 02:14:57,396
You should be very proud of him.

2110
02:14:57,470 --> 02:14:58,801
I am.

2111
02:15:01,140 --> 02:15:02,698
You still think he's out there?

2112
02:15:02,775 --> 02:15:04,003
Why not?

2113
02:15:05,245 --> 02:15:07,213
Three boys made a run for it
that night, Detective.

2114
02:15:07,280 --> 02:15:08,804
And if one got out,

2115
02:15:08,882 --> 02:15:11,976
then maybe either
or both of the others did, too.

2116
02:15:12,051 --> 02:15:15,612
Maybe Walter's out there,
having the same fears that he did.

2117
02:15:15,722 --> 02:15:17,587
Afraid to come home and identify himself,

2118
02:15:17,657 --> 02:15:20,057
or afraid he'll get into trouble.

2119
02:15:21,494 --> 02:15:23,587
But either way,

2120
02:15:23,663 --> 02:15:26,791
it gives me something I didn't have
before tonight.

2121
02:15:26,900 --> 02:15:28,299
What's that?

2122
02:15:29,269 --> 02:15:30,463
Hope.